{"tid":625067,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幾乎每年發律師信","createTime":"2018-04-11T06:36:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T22:29:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"367450b15daee67a0aed2daa87d178db66a598d5","tid":625067,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:36:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180411/20357919?_ga=2.137399344.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180411%2F20357919%3F_ga%3D2.137399344.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=kQgFSJP9XBHiOkgzvsGqHsmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=84be405b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180411%2F20357919%3F_ga%3D2.137399344.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=0ffec7a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180411/20357919?_ga=2.137399344.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n幾乎每年發律師信<br />\n<br />\n3.8K<br />\n港聞<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180411/large/a0802a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180411%2Flarge%2Fa0802a.gif&h=058e8a19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁振英<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】梁振英任內與以往特首最不同之處，就是經常就批評他的言論，向立法會議員、傳媒發律師信，當中絕大部份均與他收取澳洲公司UGL 5,000萬元「分手費」事件有關。<br />\n<br />\n梁2012年上任特首，時任《信報》特約評論員練乙錚2013年1月以〈誠信問題已非要害 梁氏涉黑實可雙規〉為題撰文，內文提及「梁氏取得政權，一半靠黑道」，結果梁即以個人身份向《信報》發律師信，要求對方撤回文章並道歉，《信報》事後刊聲明道歉，但梁向傳媒發律師信做法，引起輿論譁然。<br />\n<br />\n之後幾年梁仍不時向公開批評他的人發律師信，但幾乎全部與UGL事件有關，如2014年向揭發UGL事件的澳洲傳媒Fairfax Media發律師信，威脅若刊出報道就會告上法庭；2017年又因立會議員梁繼昌指梁因UGL事件仍受廉署及稅務機關調查，梁振英又向梁繼昌發律師信，並入稟控告他誹謗；若計及今次梁向林卓廷等民主黨人發律師信，梁為反擊外界狙擊UGL事件，幾乎每年也為此發律師信。<br />\n<br />\n■記者莫劍弦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n引條例以監禁威嚇<br />\n<br />\n港聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n又出律師信　反擊眾籌查UGL案梁振英指民主黨刑事誹謗<br />\n<br />\n港聞 5小時前"},{"pid":"2356e63b76ef054e15edd9cf52b7917dda61209e","tid":625067,"uid":37502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:50:50.000Z","msg":"當聖誕咭咁收咪得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b6abb4615d8c495169e2fff6349e7bb82195d36","tid":625067,"uid":127052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T21:04:30.000Z","msg":"邊間律師行<br />\n咁都接嚟做"},{"pid":"c925ef4a584d671970dacfc7fd0e754199fec976","tid":625067,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8b6abb4615d8c495169e2fff6349e7bb82195d36","tid":625067,"uid":127052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T21:04:30.000Z","msg":"邊間律師行<br />\n咁都接嚟做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T22:29:31.000Z","msg":"一式一樣，改個收件人就收錢<br />\n真係fatfat"}]}